title: ADVISORMAPPING
description: AdvisorMapping is a database table used to map advisors to submissions, including details such as AdvisorID, SubmissionID, AdvisorName, Region, and OfficeCode

title: JANE DOE
description: Jane Doe is an advisor operating in the West region, identified by AdvisorID ADV001 and linked to SubmissionID SUB1001

title: WEST
description: The West is a region where advisors like Jane Doe operate

title: OFFC01
description: OFFC01 is an internal office mapping code associated with advisors in the database

title: SUBMISSIONLOG
description: SubmissionLog is a database table used for auditing and tracking application submissions, including details such as submission ID, decision status, and dates

title: SUBMISSIONID
description: SubmissionID is a unique identifier for each application submission in the SubmissionLog table

title: DECISIONSTATUS
description: DecisionStatus indicates the current status of an application, such as Approved, Rejected, or Pending

title: ISACCELERATED
description: IsAccelerated is a boolean field indicating whether the submission underwent instant underwriting

title: SUBMITTEDON
description: SubmittedOn is the date when the application was submitted

title: DECISIONDATE
description: DecisionDate is the date when the final decision on the application was made

title: OFFICECODE
description: OfficeCode represents the code of the office handling the submission

title: POLICYCATALOG
description: PolicyCatalog is a database table used to store information about various insurance policies, including their codes, names, durations, premiums, and other attributes

title: SMART LIFE PLAN
description: Smart Life Plan is a specific insurance policy with a term of 240 months, an annual premium of 15000.0, and a coverage amount of 1000000.0, sold through the Direct channel

title: SALES LEDGER
description: The Sales Ledger is a database table used for tracking revenue and advisor compensation in the finance sector

title: ADVISOR
description: An advisor is a person who receives a commission payout for sales made through the advisor distribution channel

title: ONLINE
description: Online refers to the digital distribution channel for sales

title: REVENUE REPORTING
description: Revenue reporting is the process of documenting and analyzing financial income, as facilitated by the Sales Ledger

title: ADVISOR COMPENSATION CALCULATION
description: Advisor compensation calculation is the process of determining commission payouts to advisors based on sales data

title: CLIENTREGISTRY
description: ClientRegistry is a database table that stores client information including submission ID, full name, date of birth, gender, residential state, age, and civil status

title: AMIT SHARMA
description: Amit Sharma is a client whose information is stored in the ClientRegistry, born on September 10, 1985, residing in Maharashtra, aged 39, and married

title: MAHARASHTRA
description: Maharashtra is the residential state of Amit Sharma

title: RISKEVALUATION
description: RiskEvaluation is a database table used by the underwriting team to validate decision outcomes, containing information about submission evaluations, risk categories, and medical requirements

title: UNDERWRITING TEAM
description: The underwriting team uses the RiskEvaluation table to validate decision outcomes related to insurance submissions
